imdb.plot outline: Reality series. Tamara Ecclestone and husband Jay Rutland allow cameras exclusive access into their extraordinary world with three year daughter Sophia. Tamara juggles running a 70 million pound Kensington home and fleet of staff, two businesses and numerous charities with the role she clearly cherishes most - being a mother.
